      <span class="description"> Bazookanator is your go-to portal for effortlessly accessing and navigating
        PowerBI dashboards. Whether you're a data enthusiast or simply looking to keep a keen eye on your business
        metrics, you'll find viewing your data as smooth as a proper cup of tea. Ready to
        dive into the numbers? Click on the button in the upper left corner and start "The Bubble That Lasts"!</span>

      <img src="imgs/bazooka_team.jpg" alt="Fire it away">
      <button class="btn-open-popup" onclick="togglePopup()"> Questions, mate?
      </button>

    </div>

    <div class="container2">

      <h1 id="container_headline"> We have got you covered</h1>

      <span class="description"> This application is available to you 24/7. Whether you’re seeking information on HR,
        Marketing, Sales, Finance, or just curious about how much Hershey & Mars missed their investors’ targets, we are
        sure you will leave as happy as the kid below! </span>
      <img class="smiling_kid" src="imgs/smiling_kid.jpeg" alt="Fire it away">
      </button>

    </div>

